    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you use phpMyAdmin, click on <code>Home</code>, then <code>Variables</code> on the top menu. Look for the <code>port</code> setting on the page. The value it is set to is the port your MySQL server is running on.</p>\n"
